Young Man: At last... I can make my wish for all these years come true!?)
Young Man: (But why do I suddenly feel like my brain is so heavy...)
Young Man: (... Where am I!?)
Vice: Hmph... I had to force you into your inner world──
Vice: I want you to see what happens when you suppress me... when you betray me!
Vice: Before this gets ugly, first tell me why you didn't choose me!
Young Man: Although I didn't start the competition on justifiable grounds, I...
Young Man: ... I simply couldn't overlook the desire for truth and light that lay within my heart!
Virtue: Y-You truly are a good man, worthy of entrusting one's life to~~
Young Man: ... Hey. Don't give people the wrong impression...
Vice: Well, since that's the case... I'll let you two taste fury from the depths of the abyss!
Virtue: Have no fear!! Let's give him a taste of the power of true love!!!
Young Man: ... I'm begging you, stop talking!
Honest Diviner: Congratulations. The new Divination Master has arrived~~
Proud Diviner: ... Hey, you were selected from the waiting list. Should you really feel proud of yourself?
Young Man: Th-That can't be! I was clearly just one step away...
Young Man: ... Could it be... that it is my fate to remain single until I'm old and withered!?
Virtue: It's okay. You still have me~
Young Man: Enough!! I'm already miserable!!!
???: Excuse me, could you please help me!?
???: I've been looking for someone... It's already been so, so many years...
Young Man: ... Would you like me to do some divination for you? I'm afraid that you'll be disappointed.
Young Man: Because I'm nothing more than a cheat, dressed up to play the part...
???: B-But a man on the side of the street recommended you...
???: ... He said you were "the greatest Divination Master in the land"...
???: ... and that you'd be able to help me make my dream come true...
Young Man: Miss, I think you've come to the wrong person──
Young Man: You...
Teenage Girl: It's you...
Teenage Girl: Mr. Diviner, are you willing to listen to my worries?
Teenage Girl: I... I always regret what happened that year when I had to move so suddenly.
Teenage Girl: I wasn't able to say good-bye to the person I cared for...
Teenage Girl: So I often made wishes to shooting stars, hoping that one day I would see him again.
Young Man: And now... has your wish come true?
Teenage Girl: ... Thanks to you, it has.
Teenage Girl: That man was right...
Teenage Girl: You really are the greatest diviner the world's ever known!
Diviner: Master~ What happened next? Did they get married?
Divination Master: Yes. They got married and lived a blessed, fulfilling life together.
Divination Master: ... However, this is just one of the possibilities.
Divination Master: ... If someday he is possessed... and the devil in his heart stirs...
Divination Master: ... perhaps another ending to this story will emerge...
